			</td><td width="2%">&nbsp;</td><td width="44%"> Abstract
			<div style="text-align:justify;">
				<P>
					<B>Introduction</B>: This article shows the analysis of the TV newscast Paraná TV 2ª Edição, from RPC, afilliate do Rede Globo in state of Paraná, Brazil, for a week. Even though television business and in journalism on TV is going trough a natural process of changing and adaptation, the major part of population in Brazil watch television, which demands a new look from people who products content on this platform. Thus, there is no death of television because of internet very soon. TV will adapt its existing styles guided by people´s news habits, therefore.					<B>Objectives</B>: The  objective of the research is to analyze the structure of the audiovisual genre television news, but specifically television news Paraná TV 2nd Edition of the PRC, affiliated to Rede Globo in Parana. This news program airs from Monday to Saturday, at 19:15 hours .
As a practical-theoretical objectives, identifies the imaging and written forms used by television news for the construction of reports that present the best of the news.					<B>Methods</B>: The study began by theoretical analysis to then pass a practical observation. The relationship between the topics covered in the reports presented and the format of television news are also covered.
The construction of the research corpus was carried out from the selection of a TV news sample displayed in primetime locality - which transmission is procurable in any part of the State of Paraná - and multi-theme content that conveys information of various kinds.
The first stage of studies was established by monitoring the issues of Paraná TV 2nd edition for identification imagery content and formatting to be analyzed. This step corresponds to a week of observation and analysis of the issues of television news in the PRC.					<B>Results</B>: 					<B>Conclusion</B>: 				</P>
